        <h1 style="color: var(--aura-primary); margin-bottom: 2rem;">Privacy Policy</h1>
        <p><strong>Last updated:</strong> April 2026</p>

        <h2 style="margin-top: 2rem; font-size: 1.3rem;">1. Data We Collect</h2>
        <p>Nomad Budgeter is a client-side calculator. We do <strong>not</strong> collect, store, or transmit your financial inputs (income, expenses, city selections) to any server. All calculations run entirely in your browser.</p>

        <h2 style="margin-top: 2rem; font-size: 1.3rem;">2. Cookies</h2>
        <p>We use only <strong>essential cookies</strong> to remember your cookie consent preference. We do not use tracking cookies, advertising cookies, or any third-party analytics that identify you personally.</p>

        <h2 style="margin-top: 2rem; font-size: 1.3rem;">3. Global Privacy Control (GPC)</h2>
        <p>We respect your browser's <strong>Global Privacy Control</strong> signal. If GPC is enabled, we treat it as a legally binding opt-out of any data sale or sharing, in compliance with CCPA, GDPR, and the Colorado Privacy Act.</p>

        <h2 style="margin-top: 2rem; font-size: 1.3rem;">4. Third-Party APIs</h2>
        <p>Our calculator queries two external APIs to provide live data:</p>
        <ul style="margin-left: 1.5rem; margin-top: 0.5rem; color: var(--text-dim);">
            <li><strong>ExchangeRate-API</strong> — for currency conversion rates</li>
            <li><strong>API-Ninjas</strong> — for city population and income tax data</li>
        </ul>
        <p>These requests are made from your browser directly. We do not proxy or log these requests.</p>

        <h2 style="margin-top: 2rem; font-size: 1.3rem;">5. Affiliate Links</h2>
        <p>This site contains affiliate links to partner services (e.g., SafetyWing, Wise, Lexidy). Clicking these links may set cookies on the partner's domain. We receive a commission if you purchase through these links, at no additional cost to you.</p>

        <h2 style="margin-top: 2rem; font-size: 1.3rem;">6. Contact</h2>
        <p>For privacy inquiries: <a href="mailto:{{ site.email }}">{{ site.email }}</a></p>
